London Page 9 Photograph (Omitted). Photograph (Omitted). Photograph Waiting
for the bidding, LWT's Greg Dyke, left, Central's Leslie Hill, right, and
Coronation Street, a mainstay of Granada TV (Omitted).
</PAGE>
