unexpected combination of circle and rectangle (Omitted). Photograph The
Pounds 85,000 Grande Complication by IWC, which is making 50 a year and
already has orders for 350 (Omitted). Photograph Alfred Dunhill's skeleton
dress watch, revealing the intricate hand-engraved movement (Omitted).
