Prosper and the Evening Standard. Prior to Pathfinders, he was head of
planning at United Newspapers. He is the author of a novel about 'a
30-year-old stockbroker who gets involved in some shady dealings.'
Mr Pither is currently a director of Suter, the industrial holding company.
He was once on the board of the London Metal Exchange.
Pathfinders shares rose 1p yesterday to 7p.
